description:
The Five to Thirty Minute Chair is a multi-purpose side chair, which can be made
of almost any sheet material and finished as desired. This is a refined version
of an AtFAB design, which has been downloaded and locally fabricated by makers
around the world.

Two chairs can be milled from a single 4’x8’ sheet, with each comprised of 10
flat, interlocking pieces that are easily constructed and secured with screws,
pegs or adhesives.

A pair of tables can be constructed from a single 4’x8’ sheet of material. The
Five to Thirty Minute Chair can be accessorized with a 3D printed Peg & Foot
Kit, which can be found at AtFAB's [Thingiverse page][].

[Thingiverse page]: http://www.thingiverse.com/atfab
name: 5 to 30 Minute Chair
